@startuml SafeTransfer Local Deployment
title SafeTransfer - Local Deployment

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle

node "Developer Machine" as DevMachine {
  artifact "Postman / curl" as Client
  node "Spring Boot JVM\nSafeTransfer" as App
}

node "Docker" as Docker {
  database "safe-transfer-postgres\nPostgreSQL" as Postgres
  queue "safe-transfer-kafka\nKafka" as Kafka
  artifact "kcat container\noptional local proof" as Kcat
}

Client --> App : HTTP localhost:8080
App --> Postgres : JDBC localhost:5432
App --> Kafka : Kafka localhost:9092\nlocal profile
Kcat --> Kafka : safe-transfer-kafka:29092\nDocker network

note right of App
  Run with:
  SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=local
end note

note right of Kafka
  Local compose exposes:
  localhost:9092 for host app
  safe-transfer-kafka:29092 for Docker clients
end note

@enduml
